  <class_name>AddRemoveOrReplaceWindowsByFacade</class_name>
  <display_name>Add Remove Or Replace Windows By Facade</display_name>
  <description>Adds ribbon windows to surfaces on the selected facade if none exist. Removes all windows on the selected facade. Replaces all windows on the selected facade with ribbon windows.</description>
  <modeler_description>Loops through surfaces on the selected facade and either adds, removes, or replaces a subsurface.</modeler_description>
